keyTable.comment: Console: MFB release between 0-1750 ms ---> play-pause
Console: MFB repeat release twice within 500ms ---> next track
Console: MFB repeat release thrice within 500ms ---> prev track
Console: MFB release after 1750 ms ---> Network Standby
Console: MFB+Aux press and hold for at least 5000ms ---> AP Mode
Console: AUX+VolumeUp press and hold for at least 5000ms ---> Manual Update
Console: MFB+Bluetooth press and hold for at least 5000ms ---> Disable Networking
Console: AUX+VolumeDown press and hold for atlease 10000ms ---> Factory Reset
Console: MFB press and hold for at least 15000ms ---> Low Power Standby
Console: Bluetooth release ---> CarouselList-Discoverable-ConnectToLast
Console: Bluetooth Press and Hold ---> SendToDiscoverable
Console: Bluetooth Press and Hold ---> Clear Pairing List
Console: VolumeUp(+) release ---> VolumeUp
Console: VolumeUp(+) Press and Hold ---> VolumeRampUp
Console: VolumeUp(-) release ---> VolumeDown
Console: VolumeUp(-) Press and Hold ---> VolumeRampDown
Console: AUX release ---> SendToAux
Console: action release ---> Alexa
Console: Preset 1 press and hold for at least 1000ms ---> Store Currently playing into Preset 1
Console: Preset 2 press and hold for at least 1000ms ---> Store Currently playing into Preset 2
Console: Preset 3 press and hold for at least 1000ms ---> Store Currently playing into Preset 3
Console: Preset 4 press and hold for at least 1000ms ---> Store Currently playing into Preset 4
Console: Preset 5 press and hold for at least 1000ms ---> Store Currently playing into Preset 5
Console: Preset 6 press and hold for at least 1000ms ---> Store Currently playing into Preset 6
Console: Preset 1 release ---> Select Preset stored on Key 1
Console: Preset 2 release ---> Select Preset stored on Key 2
Console: Preset 3 release ---> Select Preset stored on Key 3
Console: Preset 4 release ---> Select Preset stored on Key 4
Console: Preset 5 release ---> Select Preset stored on Key 5
Console: Preset 6 release ---> Select Preset stored on Key 6
Console: VolumeUp(+) release(keyEvent: Release Anyways ---> Cancel Ramp up
Console: VolumeDown(-) release(keyEvent: Release Anyways ---> Cancel Ramp down
Console: AUX+VolumeUp press and hold will generate a repeat every 1000m ---> Manual Update Count down
Console: Release of AUX will generate ---> Manual Update Cancel
Console: Release of VolumeUp will generate ---> Manual Update Cancel
Console: AUX+VolumeDown press and hold will generate a repeat every 1000m ---> Factory Reset Count down
Console: Release of AUX will generate ---> Factory Reset Cancel
Console: Release of VolumeDown will generate ---> Factory Reset Cancel
Console: MFB+Aux press and hold will generate a repeat every 1000m ---> AP Mode Count down
Console: Release of AUX will generate ---> AP Mode Cancel
Console: Release of MFB will generate ---> AP Mode Cancel
Console: MFB+Bluetooth press and hold will generate a repeat every 1000m ---> Disable Networking Count down
Console: Release of Bluetooth will generate ---> Disable Networking Cancel
Console: Release of MFB will generate ---> Disable Networking Cancel
Console: VolumeUp+VolumeDown press and release during count down ---> PTS Update
Console: VolumeUp+VolumeDown press and hold will generate a repeat every 1000m ---> PTS Update Count down
Console: Release of VolumeUP will generate ---> PTS Update Cancel
Console: Release of VolumeDown will generate ---> PTS Update Cancel
